- handling of dirty bit (SD, FS, XS) in mstatus/sstatus

- mcpuid needs to be checked (and set appropriately on initialization) as
  appropriate for each affected instruction

- the 64-bit CSRs in the model need to be projected in 32-bit mode

- floating-point

- RVC

